# =============================================================================
# .dockerignore - giam build context, tranh leak file nhay cam vao image.
# =============================================================================

# Build artifacts
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/
**/publish/

# IDE / tooling
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.user
*.suo

# Git
.git/
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# Docs noi bo (khong can trong image)
agent.md
AI_ENGINE.md
DEMO_FLOW.md
README.md
API_DOCUMENTATION.md
CONFIGURATION.md
erd_analysis.md
erd_specification.md
cleanup_data.sql

# Secret / env (du da co .gitignore o root, chan them tai day)
**/appsettings.*.local.json
**/secrets.json
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/*.pfx
**/*.key

# Test results
**/TestResults/
**/*.coverage

# OS
**/Thumbs.db
**/.DS_Store

# Docker artifacts
Dockerfile*
.dockerignore
docker-compose*.yml
